				<wikidot:authorName>PeppersGhost</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1553042</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The anomaly was created by a group who is actively antagonizing the Foundation, so they boobytrap words and phrases that the Foundation is most likely to use. The challenge involved in rigging a word/phrase to explode is proportional to how commonly it's used in general speech h (otherwise they'd just rig stuff like &quot;it&quot; and &quot;the&quot;), but their abilities are gradually improving.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
